{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38129, "create_time": 1646183820, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "不好意思，拆那在动态清零这方面真的是赢麻了😅，无论是算人命账还是经济账。", "timestamp": 1646183820}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38134, "create_time": 1646184276, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "选不同意的，你们来说说，为了经济放开防疫的理由是什么？", "timestamp": 1646184276}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38136, "create_time": 1646184331, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "经济账怎么算我暂且蒙在鼓里，我听到的是各行各业都不好过，倒闭的裁员的越来越多，大学生工作也不好找，考公务员的越来越多。只有GDP的数字那么漂亮，官员口中的稳中向好那么好听", "timestamp": 1646184331}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38137, "create_time": 1646184354, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以放开防疫会更好？", "timestamp": 1646184354}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38140, "create_time": 1646184425, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 出口数据和贸易顺差激增，人民币汇率创新高，有没有想想为什么？", "timestamp": 1646184425}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38142, "create_time": 1646184444, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "只要学过点会计你就会知道，把亏损一个亿的企业的财务报表做成盈利一个亿，并不是什么难事，手段还都合规", "timestamp": 1646184444}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38147, "create_time": 1646184500, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 那确实，现在中国GDP全靠出口带动了，也可以说这是因为国外疫情严重，中国发了球难财呗", "timestamp": 1646184500}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38148, "create_time": 1646184509, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 汇率是真实反映市场供需关系的，总假不了吧？海外美元兑人民币都出现黑市汇率了，说明什么？", "timestamp": 1646184509}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38153, "create_time": 1646184661, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 同学你可有点天真，人民币汇率还真不是由市场决定的，外汇管制了解一下", "timestamp": 1646184661}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38157, "create_time": 1646184713, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 出现黑市汇率，说明中国确实的是汇率操纵国？", "timestamp": 1646184713}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38158, "create_time": 1646184723, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 你没听懂我说的，黑市汇率恰恰是绕过官方管道的汇率啊", "timestamp": 1646184723}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38162, "create_time": 1646184810, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 正常渠道兑换不到人民币才需要黑市", "timestamp": 1646184810}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38168, "create_time": 1646184989, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以你的理解中，黑市汇率是比官方汇率低还是高？", "timestamp": 1646184989}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38171, "create_time": 1646185058, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 那就说明现在人民币汇率是被人为大幅压低的，所以出口强劲也只是靠操纵汇率取得的一时的假象呗", "timestamp": 1646185058}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38173, "create_time": 1646185153, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以我理解反了？官方在有意让人民币升值是吗，我确实没关注过黑市汇率，不清楚是在往哪个方向变化", "timestamp": 1646185153}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38174, "create_time": 1646185252, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 美元大放水，人民币供不应求，你说呢", "timestamp": 1646185252}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38176, "create_time": 1646185263, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "出口强劲是因为欧美大量撒钱补贴，居民消费需求大增，连越南去年出口都是增加20％，再加上部分东南亚国家和印度疫情严重，暂时转移了一小部分产能", "timestamp": 1646185263}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38177, "create_time": 1646185309, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "放开防疫就是笑话，支持的人非蠢既坏好吧\n美国都一百万了，而我国人口是美国的好几倍", "timestamp": 1646185309}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38179, "create_time": 1646185386, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 要是没中国的出口，不少国家早崩了，应该对中国感恩😁", "timestamp": 1646185386}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38181, "create_time": 1646185413, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "靠制造业出口的经济体都会抑制汇率上涨的，台湾也是可以压低汇率，所以台湾的消费成本比大陆一二线城市还要便宜。近段时间人民币汇率涨是要给之后留贬值的余量，参考下2015年就知道了", "timestamp": 1646185413}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38182, "create_time": 1646185443, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re Bob: *刻意压低", "timestamp": 1646185443}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38184, "create_time": 1646185468, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 那为什么越南去年的经济增速大跌呢，越南不是一向标榜承接了拆那的产业转移吗", "timestamp": 1646185468}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38185, "create_time": 1646185476, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "因为放开防疫不是经济账和人命账，而是那些人自己选的。具体怎么算账你可以去看论文，在这儿除了对喷也讨论不出来", "timestamp": 1646185476}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38187, "create_time": 1646185591, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 这么明显的账还要看论文吗？", "timestamp": 1646185591}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38188, "create_time": 1646185626, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 真够客观的啊", "timestamp": 1646185626}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38194, "create_time": 1646185797, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "曾光最近都说了，中国最终也肯定会调整为与病毒共存，只是时机问题。众所周知新冠在老年人中的死亡率远高于年轻人中的死亡率，所以我看到美国的数字是，死了一百万，但人均预期寿命只下降了1到2岁。在自由中活到78岁，和在动态清零中活到80岁，不同的人可能有不同的选择吧。当然我也承认，美国的医疗水平更高，中国如果放开，出现医疗资源挤兑，这个差距会比1到2岁更大。", "timestamp": 1646185797}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38195, "create_time": 1646185937, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以韩国越南丹麦挪威为了经济放开防疫后，经济数据是变好还是变差了呢？", "timestamp": 1646185937}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38196, "create_time": 1646185967, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 咱们现在不谈人命，只算经济账。", "timestamp": 1646185967}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38198, "create_time": 1646185990, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: “所以不放开防疫会更好？”", "timestamp": 1646185990}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38208, "create_time": 1646186260, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 越南去年放开防疫后，工厂工人大量染疫，产能下降，订单流失，经济增长只有2.58%", "timestamp": 1646186260}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38215, "create_time": 1646186490, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 欧美各国都出现供应链问题，大量货物积压港口没有足够的卡车司机来运，政府可没有因为防疫原因限制他们上班工作", "timestamp": 1646186490}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38219, "create_time": 1646186534, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 要用动态的眼光看问题，现在别人都不当回事完全不管了，谁动不动就封城就输麻了", "timestamp": 1646186534}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38221, "create_time": 1646186632, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 中国现在99%的城市，99%的人口，生产工作节奏都和疫情前几乎没有任何区别", "timestamp": 1646186632}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38222, "create_time": 1646186654, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 现在是谁动不动就封城可能面临产业流失和消费凋敝，去年美国已经强劲复苏了，第四季度经济增速高于中国，其他国家彻底放开也是大势所趋", "timestamp": 1646186654}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38224, "create_time": 1646186711, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 最近深圳、苏州两个工业重地已经麻了", "timestamp": 1646186711}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38227, "create_time": 1646186766, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 还有很多边境城市一直都是极高强度防疫，而且不会出现在新闻中", "timestamp": 1646186766}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38230, "create_time": 1646186806, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 5, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 还有餐饮和旅游业都遭到重创，完全没有恢复到疫情前的水平", "timestamp": 1646186806}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38231, "create_time": 1646186838, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 产业流失到大量工人染疫无法正常复工的地方？那些地方的政府可是求着盼着工人去上班，为何开工率还是上不来？", "timestamp": 1646186838}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38235, "create_time": 1646186925, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Eve: 深圳苏州的工业生产停了吗？", "timestamp": 1646186925}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38272, "create_time": 1646187817, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 6, "text": "我也觉得清零最好，这疫情还是会死人的……就算是大号流感也会死很多人。对经济的影响，会死人，怎么也比不会死人要大。", "timestamp": 1646187817}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38274, "create_time": 1646187856, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": true, "name_id": 7, "text": "[tmp]\nRe 洞主: 越南早就完全躺平了…苏州工业园区已经有一些工厂生产受到影响，深圳部分区域已经开始复刻西安了", "timestamp": 1646187856}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38289, "create_time": 1646188771, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 因为真想认真研究的都会去看论文，普通人只会关心自己的健康和自己的生活是否会受影响，而不是在网上算账输输赢赢", "timestamp": 1646188771}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38328, "create_time": 1646190588, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "人在美国，一点都感觉不到疫情的影响，只觉得回国的隔离政策伞兵", "timestamp": 1646190588}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38332, "create_time": 1646190963, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Hans: 都在美国了为啥还要回来呢？争取早日入籍回来当外宾啊，听拆妮子用Chinglish说welcome to China!😅", "timestamp": 1646190963}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38334, "create_time": 1646191133, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Isabella: 很难不觉得宁在反串，客观陈述下事实，咋跳脚成这样呢？", "timestamp": 1646191133}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38336, "create_time": 1646191261, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Hans: 所以你觉得为了你自己方便应该放开防疫咯", "timestamp": 1646191261}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38347, "create_time": 1646191676, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Isabella: 不是为了我方便哈，即使还没有完全放开，我看到美国人民的生活已经基本恢复到疫情前水平，这是国内能比的？美国中过招的同学和老师大部分都表示，症状还没感冒严重，因此，从现在看来，病毒的毒性已经大大降低，国内目前绝对是过度防疫，但因为疫情刚开始时选了这条路，也确实是骑虎难下", "timestamp": 1646191676}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38351, "create_time": 1646191809, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Hans: 在国内大部分人生活也是疫情前水平啊，这个“大部分”的比例可能比美国还高。", "timestamp": 1646191809}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38359, "create_time": 1646192097, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Isabella: 抱歉，我没觉得，人员流动的自由性仍然很受限，比如春运返乡？而且各种活动都需要核酸，隔三岔五就要被捅喉咙或者鼻子总不好受吧？美国大部分地方已经取消了健康检查，即便少数保留的地区，疫苗证明就是通行证", "timestamp": 1646192097}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38374, "create_time": 1646192530, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Hans: 只要不是去过疫区并不需要核酸，基本可以自由流动，扫个健康码就行。何况大部分人就在省内活动，哪里用得着隔三差五做核酸。", "timestamp": 1646192530}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38378, "create_time": 1646192689, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 9, "text": "Re Hans: 国内物价基本平稳，美国据说通膨已经蚌埠住了？一管高露洁牙膏要10美刀😅当然也许还有很多一美元炸鸡。", "timestamp": 1646192689}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38380, "create_time": 1646192729, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Isabella: 春运返乡怎么说？基层加码动辄隔离怎么说？", "timestamp": 1646192729}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 38383, "create_time": 1646192865, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 8, "text": "Re Isabella: 有这事？我买的牙膏咋就3-5刀呢？", "timestamp": 1646192865}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null,